```

### å®Ÿè£…ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³

```python
class Company:
    def __init__(self):
        self._staffs: List[Staff] = []
    
    @property
    def staffs(self) -> List[Staff]:
        """èª­ã¿å–ã‚Šå°‚ç”¨ã«ã™ã‚‹å ´åˆã¯getterã®ã¿"""
        return self._staffs.copy()  # ã‚³ãƒ”ãƒ¼ã‚’è¿”ã—ã¦ä¿è­·
    
    @property
    def staff_count(self) -> int:
        """è¨ˆç®—çµæœã‚’è¿”ã™"""
        return len(self._staffs)
    
    @property
    def total_salary(self) -> int:
        """é›†è¨ˆå‡¦ç†"""
        return sum(s.get_salary() for s in self._staffs)
```

**ãƒ¡ãƒªãƒƒãƒˆï¼š**
